Project Management U | Description :The Borrower,through MOH, shall maintain, throughout the implementation of the Project, the PMU with terms of reference, composition andresources satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

The Borrower shall by not later than March 31, 2019, or such other later date a to be agreed with the Bank, provide evidencesatisfactory to the Bank that is has committed at least forty-five percent (45%) of the total amount of the Loan for the purposesof the implementation of the Project in accordance with the terms of this Agreement.
